body:
### Welcome to Info from friends

When our phone hangs or works slow, we delete all the unwanted pics, files & data.....

In the Same way when our life hangs or slows down, let us delete unwanted worries & get some extra space to enjoy it fully.....
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
